data.description: Introducing a stunning property with a brick and stone facade that exudes a classic charm, making a lasting first impression. This home is a perfect blend of elegance and comfort, offering an array of modern features designed for a contemporary lifestyle. Step inside to find luxury vinyl plank floors, offering both durability and a sleek, modern aesthetic. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, fostering an inviting space for entertaining and family gatherings. The entire home has been newly painted, providing a fresh and inviting atmosphere. There is a dedicated study room provides a quiet space for work or reading, making it perfect for telecommuting or academic pursuits. The upstairs area features a luxurious primary suite, offering privacy and comfort. A large game room provides additional space for entertainment and leisure activities. Enjoy the convenience of a spacious pantry/laundry room combination, designed for maximum efficiency and storage. Situated in a friendly cul-de-sac, this home promises a peaceful and safe environment, ideal for both relaxation and play. This property is a presented with modern living combined with classic elegance. It's the perfect place to create new memories and enjoy the comforts of a well-designed home.
